<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/843577-i-have-read-some-of-the-reviews-describing">I have read some of the reviews describing the book as crude. I am guessing it is because the nature of the crime. What is the level of profanity?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_843577'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F16109080-an-innocent-client">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/843577-i-have-read-some-of-the-reviews-describing">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/843577-i-have-read-some-of-the-reviews-describing">See all 7 answers</a>
