    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1204052240" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10706909179100716913"><strong>Don&apos;t waste your time or money.</strong><br/><br/>This book verifies the old saying &quot;If you can&apos;t be clever, be crude.&quot; Whether he&apos;s trying for shock value or he he&apos;s over compensating for an inferiority complex in sexual matters, the frequency of the crass sexual descriptions detracts from the story line so much that I gave up on the whole book after the first few chapters. I have no interest whatsoever in knowing how this story turned out and no interest in reading any more books by this author. John Gresham, Sh</span>
  <span id="freeText10706909179100716913" style="display:none"><strong>Don't waste your time or money.</strong><br /><br />This book verifies the old saying "If you can't be clever, be crude." Whether he's trying for shock value or he he's over compensating for an inferiority complex in sexual matters, the frequency of the crass sexual descriptions detracts from the story line so much that I gave up on the whole book after the first few chapters. I have no interest whatsoever in knowing how this story turned out and no interest in reading any more books by this author. John Gresham, Sheldon Siegel, or Scott Throw, this guy is not. Don't waste your time!</span>
